{"ops":[{"insert":"这是一个用于实现可调整布局的 Vue.js 组件，主要功能是通过拖拽或点击按钮来动态调整主内容区域和侧边栏区域的高度比例。\n\n基本用途"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"该组件提供了一个可调整大小的布局容器，包含两个主要部分：\n1. 主内容区域（resize-main）\n2. 侧边栏区域（resize-aside）\n\n用户可以通过交互方式（拖拽分割线或点击切换按钮）动态调整这两个区域的高度比例。\n\n主要功能"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"1. 高度调整：支持通过拖拽分割线实时调整侧边栏高度\n2. 折叠/展开：提供切换按钮可以快速将侧边栏折叠到最小高度或展开到默认高度\n3. 动画效果：支持平滑的过渡动画效果\n4. 边界控制：可以设置最小和最大高度限制\n5. 方向控制：支持侧边栏在顶部或底部的布局\n6. 事件回调：提供多个事件钩子用于监听布局变化\n\n核心特性"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- 响应式设计：高度会根据容器大小自动计算\n- 可配置参数：包括默认高度、最小高度、最大高度、初始位置等\n- 插槽支持：通过 Vue 插槽机制允许自定义主内容和侧边栏内容\n- 状态管理：跟踪当前是否正在调整大小、当前布局方向等状态\n\n使用方法"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"<template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  <MonitorResizeLayout "},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    :default=\"280\" "},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    :min=\"40\" "},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    :max=\"500\""},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    @onAfterResize=\"handleResize\""},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  >"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <template #main>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      <!-- 主内容区域 -->"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      <div>这里是主要内容</div>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    </template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <template #aside>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      <!-- 侧边栏内容 -->"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      <div>这里是侧边栏内容</div>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    </template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  </MonitorResizeLayout>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"<script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"import MonitorResizeLayout from './resize-layout.tsx'"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"export default {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  components: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    MonitorResizeLayout"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  },"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  methods: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    handleResize(data) {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      console.log('调整后的高度:', data)"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"}"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"\nProps属性"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- `default`: 侧边栏默认高度（默认 280px）\n- `min`: 侧边栏最小高度（默认 40px）\n- `max`: 侧边栏最大高度（无默认限制）\n- `disabled`: 是否禁用调整功能\n- `placement`: 初始位置（'top' 或 'bottom'，默认 'bottom'）\n- `toggleBefore`: 切换前的回调函数，可阻止切换操作\n\n事件监听"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- `onAfterResize`: 调整完成后触发，返回主内容和侧边栏的最终高度\n- `onResizing`: 调整过程中实时触发\n- `onTogglePlacement`: 切换位置时触发\n- `onTriggerMin`: 触发最小高度时触发\n- `onUpdateHeight`: 更新高度时触发\n\n样式定制"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"通过 `resize-layout.scss` 文件可以定制组件的外观，包括：\n- 切换按钮的样式和位置\n- 动画过渡效果\n- 调整时的视觉反馈（如蓝色指示线）\n"}],"extra":{"updator":"Austin","update_at":"2026-01-21 17:15:08"}}